{"tid":755684,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐姨風暴］談契哥婚事 「口密」唐詩詠頻爆料！！！","createTime":"2018-07-25T11:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T02:54:48.000Z","uid":56716,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"48c6e9ff4299a508192c840bea22355b22111614","tid":755684,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"唐詩詠（37歲）今日喺銅鑼灣名店坊出席TISSOT活動，詩詠以火紅色裝束現身。講到鄭嘉穎同陳凱琳婚禮日期及有BB已經係公開事（相關新聞： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LD5q0G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LD5q0G&d=91oCUQQWuPg22LfIbv5bvQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=51f578b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2LD5q0G</a> ）。<br />\n<br />\n有指唐詩詠會參與婚禮，問到佢幾時起程去峇里參加婚宴，佢話：「哎呀，未呀，朋友都係聽指引，如果真係要飛會即刻飛，<span style=\"color: red;\">我8月同9月都分別攞咗五日假，原本係自己放假</span>，唔可以講太多，係佢哋嘅事，我都係等通知，亦都冇問任何嘢，佢哋需要好大空間去處理，總之有咩搵我我就做，要飛就即刻飛。」<br />\n<br />\n至於係咪兄弟團之一？唐詩詠就話：「我唔知件事係點，交畀佢哋處理，等佢哋出聲，我哋乖乖哋聽話。」換言之隨時stand by？佢話：「由一拍拖開始每日都stand by畀佢哋，希望有呢日。（係咪傳聞中嘅雙喜臨門？）真係唔知道，唔夠膽問，因為敏感，<span style=\"color: red;\">最多三個月後我先問啦</span>。（驚BB小器？）唔知道唔好立亂問，世界上只得佢兩個知，大家估下啦。」早前已經有人率先爆料指陳凱琳有bb仲去產檢，詩詠話要等當事人親口講先至相信，唔會信傳聞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於會送咩禮物，唐詩詠就好醒目tag番個活動指會送一對錶，天長地久，愛是永恆，但好朋友低調搞婚禮，搞著身邊朋友，唐詩詠就力撐：「做朋友就兩脇插刀，咩事都支持，始終係佢好個人嘅事，佢有咩選擇我都順應，但唔知咩事就唔會問，作為朋友最好就係咁。」再三追問佢係咪八月會飛峇里，唐詩詠連番表示唔講，明顯接咗禁口令，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢都係嗰句「你知我唔講得」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180725/58484507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F58484507&d=91oCUQQWuPg22LfIbv5bvQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=aba34c06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F58484507&h=d400f361\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180725/58484507</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又話唔講得，又陰啲陰啲咁爆料，鄭嘉穎多得你呢位契妹唔少！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"863160dc2f3d1ce0a14f0a5761751cbcd60a69d0","tid":755684,"uid":44083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"老雞"},{"pid":"b10d0d1d2d4f20a95273a0ddc7a192a0a0d47215","tid":755684,"uid":75426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"唔係咪唔係<br />\n<br />\n又要答唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1325647d507a389f8af9fd2982a45f8f9d78e67","tid":755684,"uid":56716,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"863160dc2f3d1ce0a14f0a5761751cbcd60a69d0","tid":755684,"uid":44083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"老雞"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"爛臭流膿閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5624b8f0af7a8ce8757ed53e0d8bbf21915acaee","tid":755684,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1325647d507a389f8af9fd2982a45f8f9d78e67","tid":755684,"uid":56716,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"863160dc2f3d1ce0a14f0a5761751cbcd60a69d0","tid":755684,"uid":44083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"老雞"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"爛臭流膿閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f4852940bf93271821782ff9fb8baaf1c4227e","tid":755684,"uid":56716,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b10d0d1d2d4f20a95273a0ddc7a192a0a0d47215","tid":755684,"uid":75426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"唔係咪唔係<br />\n<br />\n又要答唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"扭扭擰擰，仲要叫人估下，同講出嚟無分別<img src=\"